---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout tittle="Caja de texto">
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center pt-40">
        <div class="bg-white w-[1000px] h-[600px] rounded-3xl shadow-[#804422] shadow-xl">
            <div id="back" class="absolute right-1/4 top-[20%] px-3 py-2 bg-[#804422] rounded-2xl text-white hover:cursor-pointer select-none hover:bg-white hover:text-[#804422] border hover:border-[#804422] hover:scale-110 duration-150" onclick="window.location.href = 'index.html'">
                <p>
                    Regresar
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 grid grid-cols-2">

                <div class="h-[525px]">
                    <textarea name="" id="text1" rows="5" cols="33" class="w-full h-full bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl resize-none p-4" placeholder="Escribe aqui!"></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center ">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 mb-4">
                        <p>Escribe un texto de como te sientes cuando vas al colegio, <b>se sincero contigo mismo</b>, no pasara nada con lo que digas.Te vamos a leer ðŸ˜ƒ</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <button type="submit" id="submitButton" class="bg-[#804422]  text-white py-2 px-3 rounded-3xl text-xl archivo-narrow hover:bg-white hover:text-[#804422] border hover:border-[#804422] hover:scale-125 duration-150">Enviar</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    <script src="../js/box.js"></script>
</Layout>